We are consistently and actively pursuing continual auditing to make sure Shinarium remains a safe and reliable platform for all of our babies. We believe it's firm to have innovations step by step, thus, for every new contract and service we are going to launch, CertiK and Blokminers will handle the audit before our deployment.

